<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
 <head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>New Chapter Released</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background: #f6f2fa;
      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;
    }
    .wrapper {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      background: #F6F2FA;
    }
    .card {
      max-width: 600px;
      width: 100%;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .card-topbar {
      height: 8px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg,#FF8A00 0%, #FF3D81 50%, #6F49FF 100%);
    }
    .logo {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 32px 24px 30px;
    }
    .logo img {
      max-width: 160px;
      height: auto;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 0 20px 20px;
      text-align: left;
    }
    .content h1 {
      margin: 0 0 15px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #111827;
    }
    .content ul li {
        margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    .content h2 {
      margin: 0 0 16px;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #C026D3;
    }
    .content p {
      margin: 0 0 18px;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 26px;
      color: #374151;
    }
   .story-card {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      background: #fbf7ff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-left: 5px solid #d240a8;
      position: relative;
    }
    .story-card p{
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 15px;
    }
    .story-title {
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #111;
      margin: 0;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    .story-lang {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #4a5568;
      margin-top: 4px;
    }
    ul {
      padding-left: 18px;
      margin: 0 0 20px;
      color: #374151;
      font-size: 15px;
    }
    .cta {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 10px 0 40px;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
    .cta a {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 14px 40px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg,#FF8A00,#FF3D81,#6F49FF);
    }
    .footer {
      background: #F5F6F8;
      border-bottom-left-radius: 12px;
      border-bottom-right-radius: 12px;
      padding: 50px 30px 70px 30px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .footer p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 24px;
      color: #374151;
    }
    .socials {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      margin: 14px 0;
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .socials a {
        width: 34px;
        height: 34px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        border: 2px solid #C026D3;
        margin-right: 5px;
    }
    .socials a img {
        margin: auto;
        padding: 10px 6px;
    }
    .footer .small {
      font-size: 13px;
      margin-top: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    .heart{
        color: #C026D3;
    }
    @media(max-width:600px) {
      .footer{padding: 30px 10px 40px 10px!important;}
      .content { padding: 0 10px 0 10px!important;}
      .content h1 { font-size: 16px!important;}
      .content h2 { font-size: 18px!important;}
      .cta a { padding: 12px 24px; font-size: 14px!important;}
    }
  </style>
 </head>
 <body>
  <div class="wrapper">
   <div class="card">
    <div class="card-topbar">
     <br>
    </div>
    <div class="logo" style="text-align: center;">
     <img src="https://sunoo.app/images/sunoo-logo-black.png" alt="Sunoo" style="max-width: 160px; height: auto;">
     <br>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
     <h1>Hi, {{username}}<br></h1>
     <h2>A New Chapter Has Just Arrived!<br></h2>
     <p>Continue the journey with the latest chapter from your favorite book, now live on Sunoo.</p>

     <div class="story-card">
      {{#if bookTitle}}
      <p style="font-size: 15px; color: #C026D3; margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px;">{{bookTitle}}</p>
      {{/if}}
      <h3 class="story-title">{{chapterTitle}}<br></h3>
      <p class="story-lang">Released: Today | Duration: {{chapterDuration}}</p>
     </div>

     <p>Don't miss what unfolds next. Tune in to the latest episode and let the story speak to you.</p>

     <ul>
      <li>Fresh narration, full of life<br></li>
      <li>Deeper emotions and twists<br></li>
      <li>Perfect for any time of the day<br></li>
     </ul>

     <div>
      <p>Happy listening!</p>
     </div>

     <div class="cta">
      <a href="{{bookLink}}">Listen Now</a>
      <br>
     </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer" style="background: #F5F6F8; border-bottom-left-radius: 12px; border-bottom-right-radius: 12px;text-align: center;">
     <p>Want a sneak peek? Follow us for teasers &amp; updates:</p>
